## 📋 Scripts Description

### 🚀 Setup & Installation
- `npm run setup` - Chạy script setup MCP Server
- `npm run test` - Test MCP Server installation
- `npm run validate` - Validate MCP configuration

### 📚 Documentation
- `npm run docs` - Mở tài liệu chính
- `npm run config` - Mở tài liệu configuration
- `npm run examples` - Mở tài liệu examples

### 🔧 Development
- `npm run lint` - Lint configuration files
- `npm run clean` - Clean up dependencies
- `npm run help` - Hiển thị help

## 🎯 Usage

### Quick Start
```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/mcp-server-training-guide.git
cd mcp-server-training-guide

# Setup MCP Server
npm run setup

# Test installation
npm run test

# Open documentation
npm run docs
```

### Development
```bash
# Validate setup
npm run validate

# Lint configuration
npm run lint

# Clean up
npm run clean
```

## 🔧 Configuration

### Environment Variables
Tạo file `.env` từ `.env.example`:
```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your tokens
```

### MCP Config
File config chính: `~/.cursor/mcp-config.json`

